260
00:13:08.829 --> 00:13:11.415
Oh! Well. thank goodness for that!

261
00:13:12.416 --> 00:13:13.542
[straining]

262
00:13:14.335 --> 00:13:15.711
Where the hell am I?

263
00:13:15.794 --> 00:13:18.255
- [dog barking]
- [Aoi] On the second floor of the store.

264
00:13:20.674 --> 00:13:21.884
You must be hungry.

265
00:13:21.967 --> 00:13:23.636
- Care to join us?
- Eh?

266
00:13:23.719 --> 00:13:25.888
- I...
- Do you want a super serving.

267
00:13:25.971 --> 00:13:28.390
a mega one. or an ultra one?

268
00:13:29.517 --> 00:13:30.935
A regular one. I guess?

269
00:13:31.936 --> 00:13:33.812
Thanks for the food!

270
00:13:34.313 --> 00:13:36.232
[Shin] <i>What the hell is going on here?</i>

271
00:13:36.815 --> 00:13:39.193
<i>He knows my mission...</i> [gasps]

272
00:13:39.902 --> 00:13:41.070
<i>Maybe it's poisoned!</i>

273
00:13:42.071 --> 00:13:44.865
[scoffs] <i>Well. I've spent years
building up my immunity.</i>

274
00:13:44.949 --> 00:13:45.866
[grunts]

275
00:13:46.158 --> 00:13:47.243
[exclaims]

276
00:13:51.956 --> 00:13:52.790
So good...

277
00:13:52.873 --> 00:13:54.124
[emotional music playing]

278
00:13:54.208 --> 00:13:55.543
And it's so warm...

279
00:13:55.876 --> 00:13:59.255
[chuckles] It's just like the first time
you ate my cooking.

280
00:13:59.338 --> 00:14:00.798
Just like you. Daddy!

281
00:14:02.383 --> 00:14:03.634
[Shin] <i>What is this?</i>

282
00:14:03.717 --> 00:14:05.719
<i>Such a strange sensation.</i>

283
00:14:05.803 --> 00:14:09.306
<i>In all my years on the job.
I've never felt so good.</i>

284
00:14:09.390 --> 00:14:11.392
[gasps] <i>I get it now!</i>

285
00:14:12.142 --> 00:14:12.977
Ah.

286
00:14:13.060 --> 00:14:14.228
[Shin] <i>Mr. Sakamoto...</i>

287
00:14:15.145 --> 00:14:18.023
<i>wanted to protect
this humdrum everyday life...</i>

288
00:14:19.858 --> 00:14:20.985
<i>So he quit.</i>

289
00:14:22.111 --> 00:14:25.155
[emotional music continuing]

290
00:14:30.578 --> 00:14:32.997
Mr. Sakamoto. I. um...

291
00:14:37.459 --> 00:14:39.003
I appreciate the meal.

292
00:14:41.005 --> 00:14:42.047
Hmm?

293
00:14:43.257 --> 00:14:45.885
WE HOPE TO SEE YOU AGAIN
SAKAMOTO'S

294
00:14:47.553 --> 00:14:48.929
[chuckles]

295
00:14:50.347 --> 00:14:51.765
<i>I should've known.</i>

296
00:14:52.349 --> 00:14:54.476
<i>I'm no match for Mr. Sakamoto.</i>

297
00:15:01.066 --> 00:15:02.985
[footsteps approaching]

298
00:15:04.653 --> 00:15:06.989
You wanted to see me. Shin? What?

299
00:15:10.409 --> 00:15:11.827
Pathetic.

300
00:15:11.911 --> 00:15:15.372
You couldn't get rid
of Sakamoto after all. could you?

301
00:15:16.540 --> 00:15:17.374
Boss.

302
00:15:17.917 --> 00:15:20.878
[boss] Save it.
I don't wanna hear your excuse.

303
00:15:20.961 --> 00:15:23.464
I'm begging you. let Mr. Sakamoto live!

304
00:15:24.757 --> 00:15:27.968
- [all laughing]
- [man] He's on his knees and everything!

305
00:15:28.052 --> 00:15:29.887
Why would you want that?

306
00:15:29.970 --> 00:15:31.805
Why are you covering for him?

307
00:15:32.264 --> 00:15:34.224
He means something to people.

308
00:15:34.308 --> 00:15:36.101
He's found a home in this town.

309
00:15:36.185 --> 00:15:39.313
Sakamoto threw away his responsibilities.

310
00:15:39.396 --> 00:15:41.732
He broke the rules of our world.

311
00:15:41.815 --> 00:15:43.233
I gotta kill him.

312
00:15:43.776 --> 00:15:47.404
If it's about responsibility.
then let me die in his place.

313
00:15:47.905 --> 00:15:49.073
Just let him go.

314
00:15:49.156 --> 00:15:50.240
Leave him alone!

315
00:15:51.075 --> 00:15:52.910
You'd rather die instead?

316
00:15:53.869 --> 00:15:56.580
I pointed a gun
at the person I admire the most.

317
00:15:57.456 --> 00:15:58.874
This is how I make it right.

318
00:16:01.418 --> 00:16:02.378
Fine then.

319
00:16:03.003 --> 00:16:06.256
If you put a bullet in your own brain.
I'll spare Sakamoto.

320
00:16:06.340 --> 00:16:09.093
- [inner chime]
- [scoffs] <i>Yeah. right.</i>

321
00:16:09.176 --> 00:16:11.553
<i>I'd never do that. you worthless fool.</i>

322
00:16:11.637 --> 00:16:13.180
<i>Now hurry up and die.</i>

323
00:16:13.263 --> 00:16:15.432
- [intense music playing]
- Yeah. I heard that.

324
00:16:15.516 --> 00:16:16.976
[men gasp]

325
00:16:17.059 --> 00:16:19.186
And I can't really say I'm surprised.

326
00:16:19.269 --> 00:16:21.397
[boss] <i>Oh. right! He reads minds!</i>

327
00:16:21.480 --> 00:16:22.690
Ice this little prick!

328
00:16:22.773 --> 00:16:24.692
- [Shin] <i>Only one thing to do.</i>
- [gunfire]

329
00:16:24.775 --> 00:16:26.986
- [gunfire on headphones]
- [pensive music playing]

330
00:16:34.910 --> 00:16:36.328
- [system chimes]
- [hisses]

331
00:16:36.996 --> 00:16:38.998
[inspirational music playing]

332
00:16:40.082 --> 00:16:43.002
[whirring. hissing]

333
00:16:50.217 --> 00:16:51.427
[clanks]

334
00:16:54.972 --> 00:16:55.973
[music fades]

335
00:16:59.560 --> 00:17:00.561
[clicks]

336
00:17:00.644 --> 00:17:01.895
[intense music playing]

337
00:17:01.979 --> 00:17:02.813
[gunshots]

338
00:17:02.896 --> 00:17:03.939
[gasps]

339
00:17:04.690 --> 00:17:05.899
[gunfire]

340
00:17:07.609 --> 00:17:08.569
[gasps]

341
00:17:08.652 --> 00:17:09.653
[groans]

342
00:17:11.822 --> 00:17:13.699
[man] <i>You're gonna be Swiss cheese!</i>

343
00:17:13.782 --> 00:17:15.701
Huh? What? [grunts]

344
00:17:18.162 --> 00:17:19.204
[groans]

345
00:17:22.041 --> 00:17:24.960
[panting]

346
00:17:25.627 --> 00:17:26.628
[man] Huh?

347
00:17:26.712 --> 00:17:28.047
- [inner chime]
- [chuckles]

348
00:17:28.130 --> 00:17:30.132
[man] <i>I got a great shot from up here!</i>

349
00:17:30.215 --> 00:17:31.216
- [gasps]
- [explosion]

350
00:17:31.300 --> 00:17:32.301
[groans]

351
00:17:33.969 --> 00:17:35.054
Damn it!

352
00:17:35.137 --> 00:17:37.639
- What are you doing? It's just one guy!
- [groaning]

353
00:17:37.723 --> 00:17:40.726
It's like he knows what we're gonna do
before we do it.

354
00:17:40.809 --> 00:17:42.770
That's because he's clairvoyant.

355
00:17:42.853 --> 00:17:45.230
He can read your mind
if you get too close to him.

356
00:17:45.314 --> 00:17:47.066
[man] Fan out and surround him!

357
00:17:48.817 --> 00:17:49.943
[men panting]

358
00:17:50.027 --> 00:17:51.445
[men gasp. groan]

359
00:17:52.821 --> 00:17:54.156
- [gunfire]
- [grunts]

360
00:17:54.239 --> 00:17:55.783
[panting]

361
00:17:58.077 --> 00:18:00.287
[Shin scoffs] <i>Down to my last mag.</i>

362
00:18:00.370 --> 00:18:01.914
[panting]

363
00:18:01.997 --> 00:18:03.749
<i>Guess I'm gonna
have to push my way through.</i>

364
00:18:06.585 --> 00:18:08.003
[groans]

365
00:18:08.087 --> 00:18:10.005
[groans] <i>Shit!</i>

366
00:18:10.089 --> 00:18:11.507
[music stops]

367
00:18:12.257 --> 00:18:13.759
[groans. grunts]

368
00:18:13.842 --> 00:18:14.760
[gasps]

369
00:18:17.054 --> 00:18:18.847
[gasps. shudders]

370
00:18:18.931 --> 00:18:20.057
[straining]

371
00:18:20.140 --> 00:18:21.183
<i>I'm finished.</i>

372
00:18:21.266 --> 00:18:22.434
[electricity crackling]

373
00:18:22.518 --> 00:18:24.561
[men screaming]

374
00:18:24.645 --> 00:18:25.687
[groans]

375
00:18:26.355 --> 00:18:27.689
[gasps]

376
00:18:31.068 --> 00:18:32.778
[electricity crackling]

377
00:18:33.529 --> 00:18:35.030
Mr. Sakamoto.

378
00:18:35.114 --> 00:18:36.865
What's he doing here?

379
00:18:36.949 --> 00:18:38.033
Kill him!

380
00:18:38.117 --> 00:18:40.119
[growls] Die!

381
00:18:40.202 --> 00:18:41.662
[intense music continues]

382
00:18:43.831 --> 00:18:44.998
[thudding]

383
00:18:45.749 --> 00:18:46.750
[clinks]

384
00:18:46.834 --> 00:18:48.043
- [groans]
- [man] Son of a--

385
00:18:48.127 --> 00:18:49.086
[groans]

386
00:18:49.378 --> 00:18:50.587
[clinks. hisses]

387
00:18:50.671 --> 00:18:51.505
[whooshes]

388
00:18:51.588 --> 00:18:52.631
[gasps]

389
00:18:52.714 --> 00:18:53.674
[man yelling]

390
00:18:53.757 --> 00:18:54.925
[groans]

391
00:18:55.259 --> 00:18:56.677
[man] I'll kill you!

392
00:18:57.177 --> 00:18:59.429
[shouting]

393
00:18:59.513 --> 00:19:00.430
[groans]

394
00:19:02.015 --> 00:19:02.850
[clinking]

395
00:19:04.059 --> 00:19:05.185
[groans]

396
00:19:05.269 --> 00:19:06.520
[panting]

397
00:19:06.603 --> 00:19:07.688
[grunting]

398
00:19:07.771 --> 00:19:08.689
[whooshes]

399
00:19:10.107 --> 00:19:11.567
- [whooshing]
- [exclaims]

400
00:19:11.650 --> 00:19:12.484
[groans]

401
00:19:12.568 --> 00:19:14.236
- Die!
- [man yells]

402
00:19:14.528 --> 00:19:15.404
[straining]

403
00:19:15.821 --> 00:19:17.239
{\an8}[men yelling]

404
00:19:17.322 --> 00:19:18.991
{\an8}WASTE

405
00:19:21.660 --> 00:19:22.870
[thudding]

406
00:19:25.247 --> 00:19:26.415
[groans]

407
00:19:27.040 --> 00:19:29.084
[man] <i>What just happened?</i>

408
00:19:29.918 --> 00:19:31.003
Die!

409
00:19:31.295 --> 00:19:32.963
[groans]

410
00:19:33.422 --> 00:19:34.548
- [groans]
- [knife clatters]

411
00:19:34.631 --> 00:19:36.550
Shit. Quit going in one at a time.

412
00:19:36.633 --> 00:19:38.719
- We have to shoot all at once!
- [shudders]

413
00:19:42.639 --> 00:19:43.473
Light him up.

414
00:19:43.557 --> 00:19:45.684
[gunfire]

415
00:19:47.644 --> 00:19:49.062
[screams]

416
00:19:50.814 --> 00:19:52.024
[men groan]

417
00:19:53.817 --> 00:19:55.986
[boss] <i>You bastard!</i>

418
00:19:57.779 --> 00:19:58.780
[Shin] <i>Amazing.</i>

419
00:19:59.198 --> 00:20:00.199
<i>There he is.</i>

420
00:20:00.282 --> 00:20:01.867
[thuds]

421
00:20:01.950 --> 00:20:03.619
<i>The Legendary Assassin.</i>

422
00:20:04.494 --> 00:20:05.996
<i>Taro Sakamoto.</i>

423
00:20:08.040 --> 00:20:08.874
[gasps]

424
00:20:08.957 --> 00:20:11.293
Mr. Sakamoto? How did you find me?

425
00:20:14.796 --> 00:20:16.006
- [clicks]
- Huh?

426
00:20:17.716 --> 00:20:19.509
You... You bugged my gun?

427
00:20:20.552 --> 00:20:22.262
<i>He must've put it there yesterday!</i>

428
00:20:23.180 --> 00:20:24.806
<i>He hasn't let his guard down.</i>

429
00:20:26.058 --> 00:20:27.476
Mr. Sakamoto.

430
00:20:27.559 --> 00:20:29.478
You don't have to worry about me anymore.

431
00:20:29.978 --> 00:20:31.521
I already made up my mind.

432
00:20:32.147 --> 00:20:34.566
It's over. I really am leaving town--

433
00:20:35.442 --> 00:20:36.443
Uh...

434
00:20:36.526 --> 00:20:37.444
SHIN

435
00:20:37.527 --> 00:20:38.946
An apron?

436
00:20:39.029 --> 00:20:41.281
You'll get eight hundred yen per hour.

437
00:20:41.365 --> 00:20:43.575
And if you happen to work overtime.

438
00:20:45.535 --> 00:20:46.578
it's paid.

439
00:20:46.995 --> 00:20:47.829
[Shin] Eh?

440
00:20:48.413 --> 00:20:51.124
[chill music playing]

441
00:20:51.208 --> 00:20:52.542
{\an8}- [door opens]
- [bells chime]

442
00:20:52.626 --> 00:20:54.419
{\an8}[boy laughing]

443
00:20:57.506 --> 00:20:58.799
[Shin] Mr. Sakamoto?

444
00:20:58.882 --> 00:21:01.969
Can you please
stop eating your ramen right next to me?

445
00:21:02.052 --> 00:21:03.262
- [slurps]
- [groans]

446
00:21:03.345 --> 00:21:05.722
I don't wanna mess up my brand-new shirt.

447
00:21:05.806 --> 00:21:08.809
{\an8}Huh? And our supply's
starting to run a bit low.

448
00:21:08.892 --> 00:21:10.978
{\an8}- [bells chime]
- [Hana] We're home!

449
00:21:11.061 --> 00:21:12.354
Oh. wow!

450
00:21:12.437 --> 00:21:14.690
- I think it suits you well. Shin.
- [Hana laughing]

451
00:21:14.773 --> 00:21:15.941
Oh. you think so?

452
00:21:16.024 --> 00:21:18.193
It suits you. Shin! [chuckles]

453
00:21:18.277 --> 00:21:19.444
- [inner chime]
- Huh?

454
00:21:19.820 --> 00:21:21.321
[old lady hesitating]

455
00:21:22.447 --> 00:21:24.074
Here. ma'am. Detergent.

456
00:21:24.157 --> 00:21:26.618
[old lady] Oh! How did you know?

457
00:21:26.702 --> 00:21:29.162
That's just what I was looking for.

458
00:21:29.246 --> 00:21:30.539
Thank you. dear.

459
00:21:30.622 --> 00:21:32.541
Shin always knows!

460
00:21:32.624 --> 00:21:34.543
Hey. come play with me.

461
00:21:34.626 --> 00:21:36.253
As soon as I'm finished working.

462
00:21:36.753 --> 00:21:39.089
[boy] Why? Is working here fun?

463
00:21:39.923 --> 00:21:42.843
Uh. I don't know if it is or not yet.

464
00:21:43.468 --> 00:21:46.388
But it beats the hell out of my last job.

465
00:21:46.471 --> 00:21:48.557
- [boy] Why? What was your last job?
- [inner chime]

466
00:21:48.640 --> 00:21:51.059
- [Sakamoto] <i>If you say it. you're dead.</i>
- [Shin shudders]

467
00:21:51.143 --> 00:21:54.229
Uh. I was kind of a cleaner

468
00:21:54.313 --> 00:21:55.522
for society.

469
00:21:55.605 --> 00:21:56.857
[Sakamoto] Mmm.

470
00:21:58.734 --> 00:22:00.652
[slurps. gulps]

471
00:22:01.611 --> 00:22:03.071
[children laughing]

472
00:22:03.155 --> 00:22:04.740
[girl] Come on. hurry up!

473
00:22:04.823 --> 00:22:06.450
- [bells chime]
- [Shin] Hello! Welcome!

474
00:22:07.909 --> 00:22:09.911
[theme song playing]
